item.description:
uuid 生成 UUID 随机数。
https://github.com/uuidjs/uuid https://www.npmjs.com/package/uuid 1. Install npm install uuid 2. Create a UUID (ES6 module syntax)
import { v4 as uuidv4 } from &#39;uuid&#39;; uuidv4(); // ⇨ &#39;9b1deb4d-3b7d-4bad-9bdd-2b0d7b3dcb6d&#39; &hellip; or using CommonJS syntax:
const { v4: uuidv4 } = require(&#39;uuid&#39;); uuidv4(); // ⇨ &#39;1b9d6bcd-bbfd-4b2d-9b5d-ab8dfbbd4bed&#39; const { v4: uuidv4 } = require(&#39;uuid&#39;); uuidv4(); // ⇨ &#39;1b9d6bcd-bbfd-4b2d-9b5d-ab8dfbbd4bed&#39;
